task.summary: Changelog: -Whole new UI -New functions and methods to avoid crashes -Bug Fixes -New SnackBars -New HELP ShowCase view -Removed old API levels that crashed the app, sorry, the app is now supported api lvl 21 to 26 -Added new button in drawer to check installed apps -Added new apps to the lock-down, YouTube & Reddit -Added PlayStore link in AboutMe page -Changed notification logic, now you can dismiss it using a button
-Added License Check -Added Piracy Check -New: Changed library screen
-Added License Check -Added Piracy Check -Added notification class -New: Changed library screen
-Added License Check -Added Piracy Check -Added notification class -New: Changed library screen -Removed unused comments in old MainActivity
- Disabled License Check until further fixes
- Added Sync For Reddit support,Bacon reader for reddit, Reddit is Fun,Friendly for facebook -Fixed shake sensitivity

- Seperated recent Changes and About
- Added 30 mins timer
- Added new splash screen
- Cleaned resources
- Added new app selector, not done yet.
- Added database for apps
- Added Multi Selector library in dialog

- Added Multi Selector library in dialog
- Removed Installed Screen, will bring a new better UI later
- Added anti-piracy verification
- Fixed some bugs
- Gradle version update - Disabled installed_apps screen for now - Disabled piracy Checker for now
- Added Piracy Check for beta test - Fixed lock-screen crash

Bug Fixes:
- Starting Timer even without selected apps - Selecting apps while timer is running - Lock-Time title not changing after timer is finished
Requests: - Removed package names from app selector. You got it ;)
New Features: - Removed all app restarts! You can launch the app, update, start lock-down and change shake detection state WITHOUT restarting the app! - Added colors to Alerts ( Red for selecting apps, Green for app update ) - Added new Alert when the app is updated
Others: - Huge performance improvment due to migrating all the data to database instead of sharedPreferences - Removed all redundant codes - Cleaned up code, removed all comments and useless library imports

[NEW] -App-Open Counter selection button is now working ! Select a value out of the 4 & the (LOCKED) Lock-Screen will change after you bypass your selection ! -Added new db values for the upcoming updates (stats screen) -Added version name in about screen -Added selected settings in main screen ( Selected time, selected App-Open counter ) -Added gif library to the credits [FIXES] -Fixed some bugs, cleaned code and methods -Fixed Clear All button in multi-selector, now all selections are cleared -Rearranged buttons in drawer according to priority -Made drawer color darker blue -Fixed help screen when timer is on
